    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217070/extras/b1d36d997bcf421f680f4a4fc522620e.apng?t=1730056451\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217070/extras/b1d36d997bcf421f680f4a4fc522620e.poster.avif?t=1730056451\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=120 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You could be a Hero, You Could be a Champion or Could be a Secret Ace of your team that no one understands your hard work today. you deserve something for a tiny moment. Look around first, if there's nothing that can stop you now then, Why don't we play a Little Hooky from what you are doing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217070/extras/222ab9017c0da34a2e144082af11b4d2.poster.avif?t=1730056451\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217070/extras/222ab9017c0da34a2e144082af11b4d2.webm?t=1730056451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This game is Recommended for : </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A person who's been waiting their matching queue for 5 minute.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A person who's waiting their pizza delivery but can't play decent game for now.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A person who's listening to the conversations between their friends but can't follow it.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A person who's been looking at a clock for 10 minute to something to happen.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A person who has over 200 games in their library but quite not sure what to play.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features : </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's so tiny game, It can fit on the corner of your screen!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw a Lure and hook up some fishes.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Catch many fishes and get a high score.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+25 colorful fishes and more funs.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tiny little events with special fishes.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try not to get murdered by The Ninja.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playing this game at your workplace could give you the pleasure and Thrill that</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >cannot be held responsible.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to :</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look around and make sure no one is spying on you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lauch the game and hide it well on the corner of your monitor.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A and D key for Move Left and Right.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space or S key to Reel in.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ESC key for Option and close game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >the Game supports the Controller too!</p></li></ul>",
